"12/03/2018 08:45am","80.215.40.251","0","0033788287342","maximevercruysse@gmail.com","03/05/1988","En couple","Couple de domestique","1003 CA","Dear Sir/Madam,

My partner and I would like to apply for this position - as you can see from my resumé I have spent 7 years managing a private chalet in the Haute Savoie and currently work summer seasons as a chef on a hotel barge in France.  I am originally from Belgium and Anna is English.

Both Anna and I hold clean driving licences and often drive for our work in France.  We are very dog friendly!  I have 2 children aged of 4 and 6 yrs old, they are living with their mum in France, and Anna was a teenager once and knows how they think, although admittedly it was a while ago now....! 

After more than 10 years as an engineer in the construction industry Anna moved into hospitality and has also been working on hotel barges as a hostess, housekeeping and serving at table, and as a tour guide, driving and entertaining guests on visits and transferring to/from airports etc.  We are both confident driving in snow.

I speak French, English and Flemish while Anna speaks English and a little French.  We are fit and healthy, like to run, swim and bike, ski and snowboard.  Additionally Anna is a certified yoga teacher and I am a qualified masseur.  We are mature, discreet, flexible, confident in our abilities and able to work both independently and as part of a larger team.

We are between seasonal contracts at the moment, in London for a couple of interviews and therefore available late tomorrow afternoon if you have some time to see us as we see that you have an office in Mayfair.  We are able to start work as soon as is needed and January would be perfect if you consider us suitable for this position.

Written references are available.

Thanks for your time, we look forward to hearing from you.

Max and Anna

