"02/14/2019 08:01am","92.184.108.87","0","0648447910 ","stephanemorin555@me.com","08/09/1976","Célibataire","Intendant Général - Régisseur - House manager","1059PA","Dear Madam, Sir
 I am writing to you with sincere interest in your job posting 1059 PA dated 01/02/2019 for the position of House Manager/Maintenance/Butler.
In the last ten years before my current role as House Manager of a third classified growth Chateau in Bordeaux, I perfected my management skills in taking on the responsibility in area of F&B at Hotel Les Sources de Caudalie, where I established a protocol and led a large staff, to train and set the quality of service that took place in evolution of the establishment to become a luxury Palace hotel today with a Michelin Two Star restaurant. It is with this experience that I have been able to perfect my skills and strive to exceed the expectations of a very discerning luxury clientele, with an attention to detail, flexibility and ability to react quickly with solution in all sorts of situations or demands in a warm, relaxed and courteous manner. I am very passionate about my profession and gain satisfaction in being able to touch the client, meet their needs and exceed their expectations with the attention to detail that make the difference.
My current duties include managing a small household staff at the chateau and taking care of all of the principal's and his family's needs including visitors, while they are in residence. I work on a very flexible and open schedule to accommodate the often-last minute duties of the role and am very comprehensive that this is an integral part of any role in private service.
 I coordinate and execute large scale cocktail parties and corporate events as well take care of smaller groups who are often private guests of the principal.I am in charge of the day to day running, upkeep, maintenance and functioning of the entire Chateau and surrounding gardens including the wine cellar.
